    # So we check the number of times t_i is the sum of books

    # Note that we have to check both books that are in the set and the books that are not in the set.
    # We have to check the books that are in the set
    # If the books that are in the set are not the same, then we return -1
    # If the books that are not in the set are not the same, then we return 0
    books_in_set = {}

    for i in books:

    if tot_sum < k * n:
